        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Later, the stolen car was spotted by police who signaled for it to pull over. Being a brilliant person who chose a career of crime, the driver decided to try outrunning police. Considering a power, big, all-wheel-drive car probably could easily outrun the pathetic econoboxes British police use, it was an understandable move. However, superior numbers and radios paid off as officers combed the streets and found the Bentley dumped in nearby Fulwood.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
