        "type": "image",
        "src": "__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2021/02/stolen-Bentley-Continental-GT-2.jpg",
        "width": 1920,
        "height": 1080,
        "caption": "photo credit: Lancashire Post"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "No report of the condition of the luxury car was provided, but it sounds like either the theft was done just for joyriding purposes or the criminals realized they needed to dump it before police caught them. It doesn’t sound like the people involved will swear off crime and start living an honest life. Authorities say that in the last 6 months 3 luxury coupes have been stolen from homes in Preston. That might not sound like a lot but considering how valuable the cars are it’s considerable. Plus this is a ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
